Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes an end-to-end deep learning approach, which falls under the sub-category of cs.SD (Sound). Additionally, the paper deals with classification, which is a task related to machine learning, and hence, cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also a likely sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of deep neural networks, which falls under the sub-category of cs.LG (Learning). Finally, the paper deals with audio classification, which is a task related to cs.SD (Sound).
